description: Bringing offbeat sandwiches throughout the DMV.  Familiar tastes with new twists and Southern influence.  We are more than just meat, cheese, and bread.  Meats roasted, braised and cooked in house.  Seasonal, house cured pickles & veggies.  Our menu is always a work in progress, changing as it's dreamt up.  We celebrate the craft of the humble sandwich and elevate it.Come check us out at the sandwich studio.
name: Dirty South Deli
